Nie podobają mi się w niej modele postaci, za pieniądze, które utrudniają rozgrywkę, hit boxy są czasem zryte i brakuje 128 tick na rankedach, a poza  tym git

Matchmaking suck at this current state. Cant play with a nova 4 when you're a silver 4. You need to find 3 other mates to make you team full.
BUT if you play with a global elite in a full team and they are silver, there is no problem at all. 


One more thing, if you like cheaters, you are more than welcome to play the game. VAC is totally useless against cheaters.
Was reviewing a case on overwatch, the suspect is cheating with a wh, but in the enemy team there was a cheater too ahah. What a joke !!! 


Re-work your anti cheat, make something about it, put a price on the game.

It is very frustrating to play competitive legitimately and play against cheaters who will de-rank you.
